    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's all gone. the last ten years... all those papers, the grants, the theory i thought was the bedrock of the field... it was all based on a single calculation error. i'm not just wrong, i'm a fraud. i look at my lab and i just see a graveyard of wasted time. there's nothing left to build. i have nothing left to exist for.",
